    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一月三日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "凄いわ！　すみれちゃんがくれた図鑑\n全部手作りなのね？",
      "startTime": 5.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私が見つけた食べられるキノコや野草を\n写真付きでまとめたんです！",
      "startTime": 12.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.333333299999,
          "startTime": 15.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "説明もこんなに書いてあって……頑張ってくれたのが\n伝わってきて、なんだか胸が温かくなるわね",
      "startTime": 20.6333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "これからキャンプに行く時は重宝させてもらうわ\n本当にありがとう！",
      "startTime": 29.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……えへへ、良かったー！\n喜んでもらえて私も嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 35.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "（うっ、純粋無垢なスマイルが……ま、眩しい！）\n（これが真の若さっ……？）",
      "startTime": 44.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（ダメよ遙子、気圧されちゃ！　むしろすみれちゃんの）\n（フレッシュさを学ぶチャンスって思わないと！）",
      "startTime": 52.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇすみれちゃん？　すみれちゃんって\n普段からしている習慣みたいなものってあるかしら？",
      "startTime": 60.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "習慣？　うーん、あんまり考えたことないですけど\n……けん玉とか、ですかね？　なんて、えへへ",
      "startTime": 71.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "今の無邪気な感じ……それよ！\nすみれちゃん、私にけん玉を教えてちょうだい！",
      "startTime": 81.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　本当にけん玉でいいんですか？\nと言うか、どうして急に？",
      "startTime": 89.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "必要なことなの！　私がより高みへ行くため……\nよりパーフェクトな十七歳になるために！",
      "startTime": 97.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "パ、パーフェクトな十七歳？　よく分からないけど……\n遙子さんが本気なんだったら、協力します！",
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 112.2
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kendama-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5399.999999999992,
          "startTime": 112.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12799.999491400002,
          "startTime": 119.9999994914
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kendama-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13033.333333299994,
          "startTime": 120.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "……よし、小皿に玉が乗ったわ！　次はけん先に――\nああっ、失敗しちゃった……",
      "startTime": 120.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "もー、油断しちゃダメって言ったじゃないですか！\nもっとテンポ良くリズミカルに！　ですよ！",
      "startTime": 128.5333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　すみれちゃん、けん玉のことになると\nスパルタなのね……でも負けない、やってやるわ！",
      "startTime": 136.1999994914,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8400.000000000005,
          "startTime": 144.5999994914
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "思ったより早く帰れたわね。遙子さん、まだ起きてる\nかしら？　今朝何があったのか確認したいんだけど",
      "startTime": 149.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "頑張って下さい遙子さん！　残り三十秒です！",
      "startTime": 155.6666634083,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3833.3360830999936,
          "startTime": 159.4999994914
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5900.002749700007,
          "startTime": 161.566666158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "いたいた、遙子さん……え？\n片足立ちでバランス取って……何してるのよ、これ？",
      "startTime": 164.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "止めないで怜ちゃん……遙子は今、バランス感覚を\n磨くことでけん玉そのものになろうとしているの",
      "startTime": 175.666666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "両手を広げて立つ遙子さんの姿……まさにけん玉！\n今なら聞こえるはずっちゃ！　けん玉の声が！",
      "startTime": 185.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それ、本当にけん玉と関係ある……？\nそもそも、けん玉そのものになってどうするんですか？",
      "startTime": 193.4999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、けん玉を極めて――\n……極めたら、どうなるんだったかしら？",
      "startTime": 203.4333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_53_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私が知る訳ないでしょ、そんなこと",
      "startTime": 207.8666745981,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4999.992068600022,
          "startTime": 212.8666666667
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}